* First of all i added Alcohol 120% with package , to install , for the users who doesn't have it yet .

1) install the alcohol 120% 

2) Extract the RAR File [Disc 1 + Disc 2 ]

3) you can mount or burn (USE Alcohol 120%) the CCD file that included in the Folders " Disc1+Disc2 "

4) after mount or burn , double click in the Cd , the installation should Begin

5) follow the installation , and then finish

6) run the game through the Desktop or the Start Menu
